Reasoning: The paper deals with transmission over a multi-antenna broadcast channel with partial channel state information, which is a topic in information theory and communication systems (cs.IT and cs.COMM). The use of convex analysis methods to prove that the maximizing distribution is Gaussian suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SI). The consideration of a cooperative upper bound on the sum-rate capacity suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and multimedia (cs.MM).
